Class BeanMetaFiltered<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.BeanMeta<T>
      • org.apache.juneau.BeanMetaFiltered<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The class type that this metadata applies to.

    public final class BeanMetaFiltered<T>
extends BeanMeta<T>
    Sames as BeanMeta, except the list of bean properties are limited by a BeanProperty.properties() annotation.
    Author:
    James Bognar (james.bognar@salesforce.com)
